How To gpu

install tensorflow and tensorflow-gpu in your python ENV

install official nvidia driver http://us.download.nvidia.com/XFree86/Linux-x86_64/390.87/NVIDIA-Linux-x86_64-390.87.run

install latest docker-ce https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/ubuntu/#install-docker-ce-1

#Nvidia-Docker : https://github.com/NVIDIA/nvidia-docker
sudo apt-get install -y nvidia-docker2
